"Variablennamen und Funktionsnamen folgen den gleichen Regeln. Es gibt Namen,"
" die du verwenden *solltest*, Namen, die du *nicht* verwenden *solltest*, "
"und Namen, die du *nicht* verwenden *kannst*."

#: ../../source/chapters/07_expressions/expressions.rst:107
msgid ""
"Variable names *should* be descriptive, all lower case, and if you have "
"multiple words, separate the words by an underscore. Variable names *can't* "
"start with a number nor have a space or any symbol other than an underscore."
" Here are some examples:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/chapters/07_expressions/expressions.rst:119
msgid "Good variables:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/chapters/07_expressions/expressions.rst:114
msgid "``temperature_in_celsius``"
msgstr "``temperature_in_celsius``"

#: ../../source/chapters/07_expressions/expressions.rst:115
msgid "``tree_position_1``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/chapters/07_expressions/expressions.rst:116
msgid "``tree_position_2``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/chapters/07_expressions/expressions.rst:117
msgid "``car_speed``"
msgstr "``car_speed``"

#: ../../source/chapters/07_expressions/expressions.rst:118
msgid "``number_of_children``"
msgstr "``number_of_children``"

#: ../../source/chapters/07_expressions/expressions.rst:119
msgid "``simpson``"
msgstr "``simpson``"

#: ../../source/chapters/07_expressions/expressions.rst:124
msgid "Bad variable names that still work:"
msgstr ""

